能，依賴那個來自德國的奧燒。今天，足總杯得到了，我們仿佛回到了那些年。山齊士、沙加、施治，全是我們的！簽入多於三名球員是技術錯誤嘛？是！但我們就是要簽！把想簽的都簽過來！反雲哭了：「媽的！為何不是我想的那樣？這樣的雲加怎能反？！」有的按不住情緒，奔向迷雲。有的說要堅持反雲，卻私下出濃汁了。餘下的反雲所剩無幾，迷雲表示：「我們勝利了！」"},{"pid":"177e30ca5753efac9a341a809d3ea613474992db","tid":310534,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/310320/page/2?post=2baf43df00867115225b7241103bb73486d8c608\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/310320/page/2?post=2baf43df00867115225b7241103bb73486d8c608</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟嘗試回應此POST</blockquote><br />\n要回應個post就死入個post到回應啦<br />\n特登開個post刷存在感？</blockquote><br />\n另開POST討論都要你存在感審查官審查左先?"},{"pid":"42c11b26b165b782153113327692fddfbe5e1523","tid":310534,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>計場數冇意思<br />\n2&amp;b一場出得幾多分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬係on9唔係唔知下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反你隊垃圾獌就話人ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648595df97961951978f3a9b204cadd41073cd84","tid":310534,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>計場數冇意思<br />\n2&amp;b一場出得幾多分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬係on9唔係唔知下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反你隊垃圾獌就話人ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係因為你反曼而話你on9<br />\n而係你反曼反得好on9而話你on9啊acg毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada4b2ccc2830889fd5f1e57b2313b3ca70c5d15","tid":310534,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,